title: Poker Kings Texas Hold'em 1.1
description:
ABOUT THIS GAME:

Poker Kings Texas Hold&#039;em provides hours of exciting and
entertaining no-limit Hold&#039;Em action. The user can play at a
single table or in an 80-, 200-, or 1000-competitor tournament
against computer opponents. Play offline anywhere, anytime. A
casino floor view shows players remaining in the tournament,
active tables, and active seats. The rules of the game also are
included.

Version 1.1 may include unspecified updates, enhancements, or
bug fixes.
